      • getRxnLocation

        public String getRxnLocation()
        Gets the reaction location. This string is used by BioCyc/MetaCyc files to annotate transport reactions and reactions within certain compartments. The interpretation of the string seems to be network/species dependent.
        Returns:
        The RXN-LOCATION attribute.

      • compare

        public boolean compare(Vertex v)
        Compares the member variables of this vertex to the member variables of the given vertex. In particular, compares the name, type, the mass for compounds, isReversed and the reversed reaction for reactions. Does not compare the reversed reaction.
        Parameters:
        v -
        Returns:
        true, if the vertices are equal, false otherwise.
